<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">Screen1:<br />&nbsp;.dw Object1, Object2 ...<br />Screen2:<br />&nbsp;.dw SomeObject, AnotherObject, ...<br /></div>
<br />
<br />That's what I'd do. You said you already knew the X, Y coords?

		

